title: The PokerStars.net Big Game
overview: The PokerStars.net Big Game is the ultimate high-stakes TV cash game show that sees Loose Cannon amateurs play against the legends of poker for cold hard cash. PokerStars buys each Loose Cannon into the game for $100,000, and they get to keep any profit. It's a true test of poker skill, and the best thing to happen to TV poker in years.
